## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-102"><xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain>类包含一份<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform>确定如何在创建摘要之前订单 XML 数据的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-102">The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain> class contains a list of <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform> objects that determine how to order XML data before creating a digest.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-103">使用<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain>类无论何时需要将一个或多个转换对象添加到加密的 XML 文档或签名的 XML 文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-103">Use the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain> class whenever you need to add one or more transform objects to an encrypted XML document or to a signed XML document.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-104">这两个<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference>类和<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference>类包含<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-104">Both the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference> class and the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference> class contain a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain> object.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-105">你可以添加<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform>对象传递给<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference>类通过调用<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.AddTransform%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-105">You can add a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform> object to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference> class by calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.AddTransform%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-106">你可以添加<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform>对象传递给<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference>类通过调用<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.AddTransform%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-106">You can add a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Transform> object to the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference> class by calling the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.AddTransform%2A> method.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-107">你还可以创建<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain>手动对象并将它传递到<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.TransformChain%2A>属性或<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.TransformChain%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-107">You can also create a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.TransformChain> object manually and pass it to either the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.TransformChain%2A> property or the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.TransformChain%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-108">如果你想要登录仅为 XML 文档的一部分，你可以使用转换来标识要进行签名的 XML 元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-108">If you want to sign only a portion of an XML document, you can use a transform to identify the XML elements you intend to sign.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-109">请注意，<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.Uri%2A>属性和<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.Uri%2A>属性自动创建内部转换，您可以登录文档的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-109">Note that the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.Reference.Uri%2A> property and the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedReference.Uri%2A> property automatically create internal transforms that allow you to sign a portion of a document.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e5cc9-110">有关转换的详细信息，请参阅 XMLDSIG 规范，这是可从在 www.w3.org/TR/xmldsig-core/ W3C，或请参阅 XML 加密规范，这是可从在 www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/ W3C。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e5cc9-110">For more information about transforms, see the XMLDSIG specification, which is available from the W3C at www.w3.org/TR/xmldsig-core/, or see the XML encryption specification, which is available from the W3C at www.w3.org/TR/xmlenc-core/.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
